// Starter affix set. Tiers numbered T1 (best) → T4 (worst); ilvl_required
// gates availability; weight controls relative frequency within the affix.
// Curve across tiers: weight 1000/600/300/100 at ilvl 1/20/40/60.
//
// Pool shape (matters for rare affix-count target of 4-6):
//   Weapon prefix groups: 5 (phys flat/inc + fire/cold/lightning flat)
//   Weapon suffix groups: 7 (3 element resistances + attack speed +
//                            crit chance + crit damage + movement speed)
//   Armor (helm/chest/boots) prefix groups: 4 (life + armor/evasion/ES)
//   Armor suffix groups:    4 (3 element resistances + movement speed)
[
    // ---------- weapon prefixes ----------
